# === NexName — downloads-only repository ===
# This repo publishes the README and the built releases (the Releases page), NOT the
# source code. Track ONLY the public landing files; ignore everything else so the
# source, build output, and zips stay local and never get committed.

# Ignore everything at the repo root by default...
/*

# ...then allow back only the public files:
!/.gitattributes
!/.gitignore
!/.github/
!/LICENSE
!/README.md
